name: Edenpatch
tagline: Free tool to layout, plan and track your vegetable garden
body:
### Welcome to EdenPatch.

EdenPatch is the first open source tool to plan, track and share your vegetable garden. You can find out more about [EdenPatch here](http://www.edenpatch.com).

### Authors and Contributors
EdenPatch was founded in 2015 by Venky Rao (@iraxl).

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with EdenPatch? Check out our [FAQs](http://blog.edenpatch.com/category/FAQs) or [contact support](http://edenpatch.com/contact) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
